data.description: Seller has assumable mortgage with VERY LOW interest rate! This is your chance to purchase the highly desirable Monte Carlo floor plan within the community of Portico, surrounded by lakes and green space. This unique parcel offers plenty of space between neighbors and features endless lake views to enjoy the Florida sunset from the western rear exposure. The spacious two-story home features an open layout and has plenty options for in home office, guest rooms, multi-gen living/game room.  This popular floor plan, offers a separate formal dining room and living room toward the front of the home and an additional separate bedroom on the first floor. The kitchen opens up to a large great room, has a nice breakfast nook, overseeing the lake, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a built in desk space and a breakfast bar, perfect for cooking and entertaining! The second level includes four secondary bedrooms, a large owner’s suite and a multipurpose huge bonus room. Brick paver walkway, entry and patio. Screened under truss lanai with unobstructed lake views. Portico offers a swimming pool, fitness center, tennis, basketball, pickle ball, playground and plenty walking paths
